window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The rescue on Duran Island did not go as planned. </p> <p>Jonathan Quinn knows that someone is responsible. That someone decided throwing people Quinn cares about into the line of fire in a cold-hearted act of self-preservation was a good idea. He also knows that this someone has made a serious mistake. Because when Quinn gets mad, the last place anyone should ever be is in his crosshairs. He will not stop until the guilty pay. </p> <p>Sometimes revenge is best served now.</p>"; 
